'''江東官邸'''（{{lang-ko|강동 관저}}）<ref>{{cite news|last=이|first=수경|url=http://www.rfa.org/korean/weekly_program/truth_kim_family/kim_mansion-01112010134536.html|title=김씨 왕조의 실체] 김정일의 호화 별장|work=Radio Free Asia|date=January 11, 2010|accessdate=December 12, 2012|language=ko|archive-date=2021-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201140840/https://www.rfa.org/korean/weekly_program/truth_kim_family/kim_mansion-01112010134536.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>是[[朝鮮民主主義人民共和國|朝鮮民主主義人民共和國]][[朝鲜民主主义人民共和国最高领导人|領導人]]的避暑勝地，也是最高領導人[[金正恩|金正恩]]僅次於[[龍城官邸|龍城官邸]]的的第二大官邸。<ref>{{cite news|last=Ramstad|first=Evan|url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB124295017403345489.html#project%3DSLIDESHOW08%26s%3DSB124294009528844763%26articleTabs%3Dinteractive|title=Gulags, Nukes and a Water Slide: Citizen Spies Lift North Korea's Veil|work=The Wall Street Journal|date=May 22, 2009|accessdate=December 12, 2012|archive-date=2009-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090925094339/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB124295017403345489.html#project%3DSLIDESHOW08%26s%3DSB124294009528844763%26articleTabs%3Dinteractive|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==位置==
據[[金正日|金正日]]前保鑣[[李英國|李英國]]的敘述，[[平壤市|平壤市]]周圍至少有八座領導人官邸。<ref>{{cite news|title=The Supremo in His Labyrinth|work=Time Magazine|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,201976-1,00.html|accessdate=December 12, 2012|first=Donald|last=Macintyre|date=February 18, 2002|archive-date=2013-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130731023955/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,201976-1,00.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>江東官邸位於平壤市郊的[[江東郡|江東郡]]，位於[[金日成廣場|金日成廣場]]東北部約{{convert|30|km|mi|abbr=on}}。<ref name="wikimapia">{{cite web| title= KWP Leadership Compound| work= Wikimapia| url= http://wikimapia.org/#lat=39.1989362&lon=126.0184097&z=15&l=5&m=b&show=/4824445/KWP-Leadership-Compound| accessdate= December 12, 2012| archive-date= 2011-08-25| archive-url= https://www.webcitation.org/61CZ2O6Sc?url=http://wikimapia.org/#lat=39.1989362&lon=126.0184097&z=15&l=5&m=b&show=/4824445/KWP-Leadership-Compound| dead-url= no}}</ref>[[大同江|大同江]]距其北部僅{{convert|1|km|mi|abbr=on}}。整個官邸佔地面積約{{convert|4|km2|mi2|abbr=on}}。<ref>{{cite news|last=Lubin|first=Gus|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/kim-jong-il-luxury-mansions-2010-6?op=1|title=House of the Day: The Countless Luxury Mansions Of Kim Jong Il|work=Business Insider|date=June 2, 2010|accessdate=December 12, 2012|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411131954/https://www.businessinsider.com/kim-jong-il-luxury-mansions-2010-6?op=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==描述==
官邸始建於1980年代，於1990年在金正日的命令下擴建。<ref name="FAS">{{cite web|title= North Korean Special Weapons Facilities: Command and Control|work= Federation of American Scientists|url= http://www.fas.org/nuke/guide/dprk/facility/c3i.htm|accessdate= December 12, 2012|archive-date= 2020-09-14|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200914174604/https://fas.org/nuke/guide/dprk/facility/c3i.htm|dead-url= no}}</ref>除了金正日自己的住宅，還包括了其後任妻子[[高英姬|高英姬]]、妹妹[[金敬姬|金敬姬]]、妹夫[[張成澤|張成澤]]的住所。<ref name="DailyNK">{{cite news|last=Han|first=Young Jin|url=http://www.dailynk.com/english/read.php?cataId=nk02300&num=83|title=Kim Jong Il, Where He Sleeps and Where He Works|work=DailyNK|date=March 15, 2005|accessdate=December 12, 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130516044422/http://www.dailynk.com/english/read.php?cataId=nk02300&num=83|archivedate=2013年5月16日}}</ref>該區域主要用於夏日避暑或度假<ref>{{cite web| url= http://curbed.com/archives/2011/12/21/lavish-mansions-of-the-late-north-korean-despot-kim-jongil.php| title= Lavish Mansions of the Late North Korean Despot Kim Jong-Il| work= Curbed| accessdate= December 12, 2012| archive-date= 2012-06-28| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120628172353/http://curbed.com/archives/2011/12/21/lavish-mansions-of-the-late-north-korean-despot-kim-jongil.php| dead-url= no}}</ref>，或高層內部聚會宴飲。<ref name="FAS"/>外有一精心設計的花園，環繞著諸多湖泊。另有大量的客房和一宴會廳。<ref name="Independent">{{cite news|last=Prynne|first=Miranda|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/north-korea-uncovered-palaces-labour-camps-and-mass-graves-1711573.html|title=North Korea uncovered: Palaces, labour camps and mass graves|work=The Independent|date=June 21, 2009|accessdate=December 12, 2012|archive-date=2021-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307232604/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/north-korea-uncovered-palaces-labour-camps-and-mass-graves-1711573.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>作為閒人免入的禁地，整個區域裝設了二重防護欄<ref>{{cite web|title= North Korea by Google Earth: Kim Jong Il’s Largest Palace|work= One Free Korea|url= http://freekorea.us/2007/04/10/its-good-to-be-the-king-kim-jong-ils-home-and-office-by-google-earth/|accessdate= December 12, 2012|archive-date= 2020-06-23|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200623093156/https://freekorea.us/2007/04/10/its-good-to-be-the-king-kim-jong-ils-home-and-office-by-google-earth/|dead-url= no}}</ref>，其警衛哨所和檢查站在衛星圖片上也清晰可見。<ref>{{cite web|title= North Korea Secret Places|work= LiveLeak|url= http://www.liveleak.com/view?i=ce1_1344695232&comments=1|accessdate= December 12, 2012|archive-date= 2017-03-13|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170313055129/https://www.liveleak.com/view?i=ce1_1344695232&comments=1|dead-url= no}}</ref>金正日的前廚師[[藤本健二|藤本健二]]曾服務於該官邸的客房，提供了部分1989年拍攝的照片。<ref name="DailyNK"/>衛星圖片分析顯示該區域自2006年起開始進行大規模改造，增設了新的建築和火車站。<ref>{{cite web|title= Kim family Kangdong compound updated|work= North Korea Economy Watch|url= http://www.nkeconwatch.com/2012/03/23/kim-family-kangdong-compound-updated/|accessdate= December 12, 2012|archive-date= 2021-01-31|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210131131956/http://www.nkeconwatch.com/2012/03/23/kim-family-kangdong-compound-updated/|dead-url= no}}</ref>距[[脫北者|脫北者]]反映，為了加強偶像化工作，距此官邸和[[檀君陵|檀君陵]]不遠的江東郡香木里又打造起了金正恩的出生地<ref>{{cite news|last=Kim|first=Yong Hun|url=http://www.dailynk.com/english/read.php?cataId=nk00100&num=7975|title=Idolization of Kim Jong Eun Began in January 2009|work=DailyNK|date=July 22, 2011|accessdate=December 12, 2012|archive-date=2015-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923212600/http://www.dailynk.com/english/read.php?cataId=nk00100&num=7975|dead-url=no}}</ref>，儘管其實際出生地是在[[平安北道|平安北道]]的[[昌城郡|昌城郡]]。<ref>{{cite news|last=Shin|first=Joo Hyun|url=http://www.dailynk.com/english/read.php?cataId=nk00100&num=6907|title=Kim Jong Eun Birth Manipulation Well Underway|work=DailyNK|date=October 14, 2010|accessdate=December 12, 2012|archive-date=2012-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120112045208/http://www.dailynk.com/english/read.php?cataId=nk00100&num=6907|dead-url=no}}</ref>

